     5‚Üí# Summary ‚Ä¶
    16‚Üí# Contents ‚Ä¶
    43‚Üí# Motivation ‚Ä¶
    98‚Üí# Guide-level explanation ‚Ä¶
   495‚Üí# Reference-level explanation ‚Ä¶
   502‚Üí### Don't break anything
   504‚ÜíAllow structured logging to be added in the current `0.4.x` series of `log`. This gives us the option of including structured logging in an `0.4.x` release, or bumping the minor crate version without introducing any actual breaking changes.
   505‚Üí
